MOVE RIGHT IN and enjoy this easy maintenance, well maintained, 3 bedroom, 1.5 bathroom home located in a wonderful, residential neighborhood, conveniently located to schools, shopping, recreational activities, ...featuring a spacious living and dining area, with glass doors leading to a relaxing, sun room, oak kitchen, 3 nice sized bedrooms with closets, hardwood flooring, basement with rec. room, half bath/laundry/utility area, attached, oversized two car garage with large, workshop area, some newer windows, and newer hot water tank. and much more.  DON'T MISS OUT!  
ALL REASONABLE OFFERS WILL BE CONSIDERED!
